2026-03-27T16:55:40.530Z JOY-0060 item.created "Inline comments in .gitignore break ignore patterns" [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
2026-03-27T16:55:47.521Z JOY-0060 comment.added "Root cause: git .gitignore does not support inline comments. A '#' in the middle of a line is treated as part of the pattern. Fix: move comments to lines above the entries, or remove them entirely since the joy:start/joy:end block is already self-documenting." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
